  "description": "<i>Hibernatus</i> is a text adventure game. The protagonist of the game is Zen who wakes up early from hibernation in a lunar base. The supervision is carried out by two robots that have been damaged as a result of radiation. Xeran has a damaged power cell, and Yorg has broken identification system by which he attacks all living beings. The player wanders around the base looking for useful items necessary to fix Xeran and equip the space shuttle. He may collect items and use them at the appropriate places. During the game the player may regenerate his life energy in a special machine and has to consume the food to stay in good shape. The final goal is to escape from the base without being killed by Yorg. <br><br>\nThe text in the game is supplemented by detailed colorful graphics. The player performs activities using text commands. The game accepts simple sentences consisting of a verb and object names.",
